{"type":"text","timestamp":1782887214867,"sessionID":"ses_0e3a7cbdbffepKwi4Ygk8sEv0I","part":{"id":"prt_f1c5be514001fggNcE0m4qteut","messageID":"msg_f1c5bba80001L9j5LWeNv4i2Xv","sessionID":"ses_0e3a7cbdbffepKwi4Ygk8sEv0I","type":"text","text":"I have enough evidence to write the lineage artifacts. The synthesis will recommend: external-shell smoke first, orchestrate-to-deep routing unification next, a prompt-transform enforcement plugin as a guardrail, and FIX-5 unpark only if external smoke/benchmark shows route-proof failures or persistent latency/stuck regressions.","time":{"start":1782887212308,"end":1782887214864},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02dc398597cf38e6016a44b32c4ec48191be26fbc3cddf813a","phase":"commentary"}}}}
